OL,12,G1830 The Big Bang Theory
OL,13,     FThe Big Bran Hypothesis. Leonard
OL,14,     Fvolunteers to sign for a package
OL,15,     Fto make a good impression on
OL,16,     FPenny, but things go terribly awry
OL,17,     Fwhen he enlists Sheldon for help.
