OL,5,G1900 The Big Bang Theory
OL,6,     FThe Fuzzy Boots Corollary. Leonard
OL,7,     Fis depressed to learn that Penny
OL,8,     Fis dating someone. Encouraged by
OL,9,     Fhis friends and fellow scientists,
OL,10,     Fhe asks a colleague out on a date.
OL,11,     FS1, Ep3
OL,12,G1930 The Big Bang Theory
OL,13,     FThe Luminous Fish Effect. Sheldon
OL,14,     Fgets fired and explores what life
OL,15,     Fhas to offer outside physics,
OL,16,     Fleaving Leonard to take drastic
OL,17,     Faction to snap his friend out of
OL,18,     Fhis funk. S1, Ep4
